OL,4,C'changed the life I could have had'
OL,6,FThe 45-year-old, from Seaham, says
OL,7,Fthat living with the liver infection,
OL,8,Fand its repercussions, have affected
OL,9,Fevery aspect of his life.
OL,11,F"I could have had the career that I
OL,12,Fwanted", he told ITV Tyne Tees. "I
OL,13,Fwouldn't have had the stigma, the
OL,14,Fhealth issues that I've got now."
OL,16,FMr Fox was speaking on the day
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/9
