OL,4,C'changed the life I could have had'
OL,6,FAmong the inquiry findings was that
OL,7,Frisks around the infected blood
OL,8,Fproducts were "well-known" decades
OL,9,Fbefore they were used on patients in
OL,10,Fthe UK.
OL,12,FDespite the passage of time, Mr Fox is
OL,13,Fnow looking for individuals to take
OL,14,Fresponsibility for their role in what
OL,15,Fhappened.
OL,17,F"We want people to come forward, we
OL,18,Fwant names," he continued.
