OL,3,CContaminated blood victim says scandal
OL,4,C'changed the life I could have had'
OL,6,F"We want people to actually say 'I am
OL,7,Fsorry' that we did this,' not 'I am
OL,8,Fsorry for what you went through'."
OL,10,FMr Fox was born with the bleeding
OL,11,Fdisorder Von Willebrand disease, which
OL,12,Fmeans his blood is unable to clot
OL,13,Fproperly, leaving him at risk of
OL,14,Fsevere bleeds.
OL,16,FHe was one of many patients with
OL,17,Fhaemophilia and similar disorders who
OL,18,Fwere given a treatment using blood
OL,19,Fplasma, imported largely from the
OL,20,FUnited States.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/9
