OL,4,C'changed the life I could have had'
OL,6,FThe product was made from commercial
OL,7,Fdonations, with many of those donors
OL,8,Fcoming from high risk groups such as
OL,9,Fdrug addicts.
OL,11,FAs a result, entire batches of
OL,12,Ftreatment were infected with the HiV
OL,13,Fand hepatitis C viruses.
OL,15,FConcerns over the safety of these
OL,16,Fimported treatments were raised even
OL,17,Fbefore Mr Fox was born.
