OL,3,CContaminated blood victim says scandal
OL,4,C'changed the life I could have had'
OL,6,FHe said he is 'angry' that those fears
OL,7,Fwere not acted upon, adding: "They've
OL,8,Flet us down big time, especially when
OL,9,Fthey're supposed to be there to
OL,10,Fprotect us and make us well."
OL,12,FMr Fox's health problems have now been
OL,13,Fcompounded by a heart condition.
OL,15,FAlthough it cannot be proven, he
OL,16,Fbelieves it is linked to antiviral
OL,17,Fdrugs he was required to take to treat
OL,18,Fthe hepatitis C.
