OL,3,CContaminated blood victim says scandal
OL,4,C'changed the life I could have had'
OL,6,FHe said he is now forced to take
OL,7,Fextreme care, with exercise limited to
OL,8,Fa single ten minute walk every few
OL,9,Fdays.
OL,11,FAsked whether he ever allows himself
OL,12,Fto imagine what life could have been
OL,13,Flike if he had not received
OL,14,Fcontaminate blood products, his answer
OL,15,Fwas uniquivocal.
OL,17,F"All the time," he said. "It's every
OL,18,Fmorning waking up and thinking - how
OL,19,Flong have you really got left?"
