OL,4,C'changed the life I could have had'
OL,6,FMr Fox is a man who gets huge pleasure
OL,7,Ffrom simply having his wife Stacy and
OL,8,Fwider family around him.
OL,10,FHowever, he said it is a joy which
OL,11,Fcomes with a burden.
OL,13,FHe explained: "Having the pressure of
OL,14,Fknowing whether you're going to be
OL,15,Fhere to see your kids grow up or your
OL,16,Fgrandkids grow up, it's awful thinking
OL,17,Flike that."
